"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 382, \"end\": 388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999193582912, \"rank\": 7.847006431131563e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The South Africanwomen's hockey teamcompeting at theParis Olympics 2024had to resort tocrowdfundingin order to make their way to France, as reported byThe South African website.\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 568, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 520, \"end\": 526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999193582912, \"rank\": 7.847006431131563e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the latest Paris Olympics 2024 news, bookmarkThe South African website'sdedicated section  Although they have not yet met their funding goal, the players have persevered with their preparations.\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With their available fund, the team recently embarked on an Asian exposure tour, which culminated in India.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 830, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Football_Confederation\", \"score\": 0.9998262886398634, \"rank\": 0.00010519231769067546, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Football_Confederation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Football_Confederation\"}, {\"begin\": 871, \"end\": 876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9411236099056807, \"rank\": 0.05931642383334278, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, head coachGiles Bonnethas rued missed opportunities for further match practice due to the lack of finances.\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Funding has been our biggest challenge, we have had to withdraw from three events, which means about 30 test matches of experience have been lost to this group,\\\" Bonnet toldThe Times of India.\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1190, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On top of that we have not been able to train in a high-performance environment as frequently as we would have liked.\\\"\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1311, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"South Africa have selected16women (and two reserves) as well as a four-person strong management team for the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1313, \"end\": 1325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4089558523141843e-12, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taheera Augousti, Quanita Bobbs, Stephanie Botha, Dirkie Chamberlain, Erin Christie, Kayla de Waal, Paris-Gail Isaacs, Marie Antoinette Louw, Ongeziwe Mali, Ntsopa Mokoena, Edith Molikoe, Kristen Paton, Hannah Pearce, Celia Seerane, Anelle van Deventer, Onthatile Zulu  Reserves:\\u00a0Aphiwe Dimba, Kayla Swarts  Management:Lynn Abrahamse, Giles Bonnet, Marcelle Keet, Wayne Lombard  Currently ranked18thin the world, the South African women's team faces a formidable challenge at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1457, \"end\": 1470, \"title\