n_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2342, \"end\": 2355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9601257932882222, \"rank\": 0.03727220896130567, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2396, \"end\": 2401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.7518883893566234, \"rank\": 0.3296673374602905, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2407, \"end\": 2409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8332610790468545e-35, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bonnet has set his team the target of finishing between fifth and eighth place this time around.\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2616, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Just to put things into perspective, the USA received $1 million for their programme to Paris,\\\" Bonnet toldgsport.co.zain April.\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2660, \"end\": 2663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9098829240625077, \"rank\": 0.06647970363941905, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2707, \"end\": 2712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5066545735056848e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is equal to almost R18.5 million.\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We could run a fully professional programme for four years on that value.\\\"\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2863, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The SA women's hockey team has had the good fortune of receiving financial support via CEO:MCSA & Showmax at MultiChoice Group LtdMarc Juryover the past two years, while SuperSport Schools andKelvin Wattrecently helped the squad travel to China and India.\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 3120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2869, \"end\": 2871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8332610790468545e-35, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 2974, \"end\": 2985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MultiChoice\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"MultiChoice\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MultiChoice\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MultiChoice\"}, {\"begin\": 3104, \"end\": 3109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6908900616460454, \"rank\": 0.29159495100008553, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3114, \"end\": 3119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9411236099056807, \"rank\": 0.05931642383334278, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There have also been hockey people whom have given up their time to source funding for the team and for this we are very grateful, it has kept our program going,\\\" Bonnet acknowledged.\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3306, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheSouth African women's hockey sidecontinues to dominate in Africa and is the only team from the continent heading to France.\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3317, \"end\": 3330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women_in_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"African women\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women_in_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women_in_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 3427, \"end\": 3433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999193582912, \"rank\": 7.847006431131563e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 10 Africa Cup of Nations and African Games tournaments since 1994, the women's team has taken gold in all of them.\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3553, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3468, \"end\": 3481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999052338397, \"rank\": 9.413703927591842e-08, \"text\": \"African Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's on the global stage where the side has struggled.\", \"from\": 3555, \"to\": 3613, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's impossible to compete with other countries, the small details will always be missing,\\\" Bonnet added.\", \"from\": 3615, \"to\": 3721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The talent exists in our country but once they finish school the gap wi